AI SOC Analyst 🛡️
Automated security incident analysis powered by Claude AI + Microsoft Sentinel

An AI-powered SOC analyst that connects to Microsoft Sentinel, automatically investigates security incidents, maps attacks to MITRE ATT&CK, and generates professional incident reports — just like a Tier 1 SOC analyst, running 24/7.


What It Does
Connects to Microsoft Sentinel via API and pulls live incidents
Investigates each alert using Claude AI with 10 years of SOC analyst context
Classifies threats: True Positive / False Positive / Benign Positive
Maps attacks to MITRE ATT&CK techniques automatically
Generates professional Markdown and HTML incident reports
Interactive mode for follow-up questions about any incident


