Setup
1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ai-soc-analyst

cd ai-soc-analyst
2. Install dependencies
pip install anthropic requests python-dotenv
3. Configure Azure App Registration
In Azure Portal:

Go to App Registrations → New Registration
Under Certificates & Secrets → create a Client Secret (copy the Value)
Assign the app the Microsoft Sentinel Reader role on your workspace
4. Set environment variables
cp .env.example .env

# Fill in your credentials in .env
5. Run
# Analyse last 5 incidents

python main.py --limit 5

# Interactive mode — ask follow-up questions after each incident

python main.py --limit 3 --interactive


